RELEASE NOTES for BANDIT
========================

This is the release "1.4.z" of the BANDIT toolkit.
This is a "DEVELOPMENT" release.

Visit https://phy.wiki for more information.


MAJOR CHANGES in 1.4
====================

* Refactored "bandit help"
* Added support for Bash completion
* Add bandit.env in BANDIT_HOME
  To change the active BANDIT instance issue "source bandit.env" instead of "source bin/bandit-set"
  